Package application

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Customizable
    This interface allows us to add and remove Objects, like add-ins to Coffee or donuts to order.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Coffee
    This class holds properties of Coffee objects like add-ins, size, quantity
    CoffeeController
    This class is a Controller for the Coffee menu and allows users to add Coffee to their order.
    CurrentOrderController
    This Controller class is for the current order menu and allows for storing and manipulation of the user's order of Coffee and/or Donuts.
    Donut
    This class holds properties of the Donut object, such as type, flavor, quantity.
    Main
    This class serves as a driver for the GUI.
    MenuItem
    This class holds the properties of an Object representing a Menu Item, such as Coffee or Donuts.
    MMController
    This class is the controller for the Main Menu and allows for data to be manipulated based on the user's actions
    Order
    This class provides the functionality of an Order, that may or may not be made up of multiple or singular instances of the MenuItem class
    orderingDonutController
    This controller class provides the functionality for ordering donuts.
    StoreOrders
    This class provides the functionality of managing multiple orders as well as other features.
    StoreOrdersController
    A controller class that provides the functionality to manage multiple orders This is the controller class of the "Store orders page.fxml" Window.
